    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Mother&apos;s Influence Reaches Into Eternity</strong>&mdash;The sphere of the mother may be humble; but her influence, united with the father&apos;s, is as abiding as eternity. Next to God, the mother&apos;s power for good is the strongest known on earth.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">1<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"HR 3-1-1880\" data-link=\"440.44\">Good Health, March 1, 1880, par. 12</span>.</span></a></sup>",
