    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>The World&apos;s Debt to Mothers</strong>&mdash;The day of God will reveal how much the world owes to godly mothers for men who have been unflinching advocates of truth and reform&mdash;men who have been bold to do and dare, who have stood unshaken amid trials and temptations; men who chose the high and holy interests of truth and the glory of God before worldly honor or life itself.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">9<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"ST 11-3-1881\" data-link=\"820.3829\">The Signs of the Times, October 11, 1910</span>.</span></a></sup>",
